nfts.name: Red Shift
nfts.description:
The light they send, once bold and blue, now frail, A whisper stretched thin by cosmic flight, Reddened by miles that time will never trail, Galaxies receding, lost to sight.

Each photon stretched, a testament to space, The universe unfurls, its vastness known, By these faint hues, a language time can trace, Of origins where stars were freshly sown.

A Doppler sigh, a cosmic lullaby, Of ancient light that paints the distant sky, Redshift speaks volumes, though its voice is low, Whispering tales of where we used to be, A universe forever on the go, An echo stretched for all eternity.
